title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should display in the data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned. Currently, the output parameter is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 
1. Go to the query result page. 
2. Observe that no data is returned. 
3. Open the edit data set dialog. 
4. Verify that the output parameter is not displayed in the dialog.
